  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a twisted psychological horror experience where you must uncover the dark secrets of an abandoned hospital and face nightmarish monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234510/extras/590c3f0311ef7065fcdba759f4814615.avif?t=1735290948\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234510/extras_big/590c3f0311ef7065fcdba759f4814615.avif?t=1735290948 width=800 height=376 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delusional Mind includes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-person survival horror</strong> with puzzle-solving and intense combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive storyline</strong> filled with mystery, psychological horror, and supernatural elements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration and crafting</strong> to survive the haunted environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jump scares and eerie atmosphere</strong> that keep you on edge.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234510/extras/e27b402f3a492a6bec457c7d6cbdf17c.avif?t=1735290948\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234510/extras_big/e27b402f3a492a6bec457c7d6cbdf17c.avif?t=1735290948 width=800 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solve Mysteries:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234510/extras/e0238ec33317a53d336caf5e8fc58a7c.avif?t=1735290948\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234510/extras_big/e0238ec33317a53d336caf5e8fc58a7c.avif?t=1735290948 width=800 height=376 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mature Content Description:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contains violence, blood, gore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
